categories: Category:Plants of the Outer Rim Territories

nodes.text: Dune-cactus, sometimes referred to simply as "cactus" was a species of plant found in the deserts of Aduba-3. It was the largest living thing Jimm Doshun had shot at with his blaster prior to joining the Sprites. Han Solo did not consider the dune-cactus to be fit for eating.
